  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2004-07-13", 
    "text": "Requires the Consumer Product Safety Commission, within six months of enactment of this Act, to promulgate a rule declaring mercury-containing toys to be banned hazardous products under the Consumer Product Safety Act. Defines \"mercury-containing toy\" as any toy or other product that contains mercury and is designed primarily for or marketed primarily to children."
